                <h2>Privacy Policy</h2>
                <p>
                    <strong>Collecting of personal information</strong>
                </p>
                
                <p>
                    Movement Martial Arts will not collect or monitor any personal information about an individual without their consent.
                </p>
                
                <p>
                    The only personal information collected is what is provided voluntarily by a member or prospective member.
                </p>
                
                <p>
